{"tid":1679362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有感黑警打壓新聞自由。有關記者証發牌問題","createTime":"2019-10-28T07:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:23:32.000Z","uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6413462cdf12d90f6197d55eb4afdea28496d17b","tid":1679362,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"睇番黑警呢排不停打壓新聞自由。又放風要有黑警認証先當係記者。我覺得連日黎警暴對記者既行動係為左認証鋪頭。我認為唔應該由黑警做主導。如果唔係佢地濫權方式會越黎越大。我認為可以整個非官方既認証機構。由佢發出認可證明。再同黑警溝通由佢地負責做管理。如同其他發牌機構一樣。可以獨立分出黎。黑警只有查詢權。"},{"pid":"8ffed8b19e4be0314aa4e3b758175f868b04c936","tid":1679362,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2177ccabd955004cd6b5f024242095ead3fdc10a","tid":1679362,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"你唔撚知有記協？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"e7f8a14907a1861af1fe378c4dea0ff87341528f","tid":1679362,"uid":114064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"又有5手<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"1f15b7475dfa58d387e25a37cc46de24042d5280","tid":1679362,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2177ccabd955004cd6b5f024242095ead3fdc10a","tid":1679362,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"你唔撚知有記協？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"最幣記協無同黑警溝通。記協只係協會性質。無實際公認認証權"}]}